  "plan": "## SNPFileCreator_1chip GenePattern Module — Implementation Plan\n\n### 1. Overview\nSNPFileCreator_1chip is a GenePattern module that Processes Affymetrix SNP probe-level data into expression values\n\n### 2. Parameters\nThe module exposes 11 parameters:\n- Required: chip.type, normalization.method, reference.method, model.method, allele.specific, sort.snp.file, output.file, output.file.format\n- Optional: network.directory.name, zip.file, reference.file\n\n### 3. Command Line\n```\n<java> <java_flags> -cp <libdir>snp.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-math-1.1.jar<path.separator><libdir>Jama-1.0.1.jar<path.separator><libdir>log4j-1.2.13.jar<path.separator><libdir>gp-modules.jar edu.mit.broad.cg.modules.PreProcess.PreProcess -lib<libdir> -cdf<chip.type> -dir<network.directory.name> -zip<zip.file> -rmt<reference.method> -ref<reference.file> -out<output.file> -mmt<model.method> -oclno -olcyes -txtno -nmt<normalization.method> -gifgenome.info.6.0_build35 -srt<sort.snp.file> -als<allele.specific> -fmt<output.file.format> -log<libdir>log4j.properties\n```\n\n### 4. Docker Image\nDocker image: \n\n### 5. Validation Strategy\n- Validate all required parameters are provided\n- Validate file formats match expected extensions\n- Check parameter value ranges where applicable\n\n### 6. Implementation Roadmap\nPhase 1: Wrapper script implementation\nPhase 2: Docker container setup\nPhase 3: Parameter validation and error handling\nPhase 4: Testing and documentation",
  "wrapper_script": "snp.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-math-1.1.jar<path.separator><libdir>Jama-1.0.1.jar<path.separator><libdir>log4j-1.2.13.jar<path.separator><libdir>gp-modules.jar",
  "command_line": "<java> <java_flags> -cp <libdir>snp.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-math-1.1.jar<path.separator><libdir>Jama-1.0.1.jar<path.separator><libdir>log4j-1.2.13.jar<path.separator><libdir>gp-modules.jar edu.mit.broad.cg.modules.PreProcess.PreProcess -lib<libdir> -cdf<chip.type> -dir<network.directory.name> -zip<zip.file> -rmt<reference.method> -ref<reference.file> -out<output.file> -mmt<model.method> -oclno -olcyes -txtno -nmt<normalization.method> -gifgenome.info.6.0_build35 -srt<sort.snp.file> -als<allele.specific> -fmt<output.file.format> -log<libdir>log4j.properties",
